{
  "stem": "3874.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So going to France really was a very pleasant thing for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived in France through Strasbourg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember the border crossing, and kids making comments-- my god, we could've taken all kinds of things with us, you know, jewelry, and money and whatever, because we weren't really searched.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was this date?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March 14, 1939.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived in-- we arrived in Paris, at the train station, and were taken to a-- by buses-- to a-- well, no.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We arrived-- yeah, we arrived in Paris, and were taken to-- first to a Rothschild hospital for approximately three or four days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where, amongst other things there, they tried to give us-- tried to give us exams, physical exams.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they really tried to clean us out by giving us all laxatives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember the first night with-- with all of us trying to use the one or two bathrooms, it was a mess.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after that, what they did is, after approximately three or four days, we were sent to an old cloister, and I believe it was run by French organization called called, Oeuvre de Secours aux Enfants.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which means, it's an organization which helps children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The abbreviation is OSE-- and the German pronunciation is Oh-zay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So amongst our whole group, everybody calls it the Oh-zay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when I say Oh-zay, that's what it means, is this particular French organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were sent to a place which was an old cloister, and it was at the outskirts of Paris, and it was called, Chateau Maubuisson.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were there approximately one month.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But while we were there, other children started coming in, primarily children from Berlin, from a Berlin transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember a transport from Frankfurt that came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, you know, kids are funny.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
